    "description_long": "This object is a circular speed limit sign displaying the number '20' in bold black numerals on a white background, encircled by a thick red border. The sign is mounted atop a slender, vertical pole that appears to be made of metal and is dark gray in color. The face of the sign is smooth and flat, with the rear side being plain and unmarked. The pole is simple and cylindrical, lacking any decorative features or additional attachments. The sign is designed to be highly visible to drivers and pedestrians, with contrasting colors for maximum legibility. There is no visible environmental context or mounting base shown in the images.",
